<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī jayābhyudaya śāli 
<lb n="2" break="no"/>vāhana śakavarṣaṁbulu <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 
<lb n="3"/>1420 Anēṭi kālayukti saṁvvatsa 
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ra jyēṣṭha ba 12 śa <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> gaṁṭṭa yeṟamanā 
<lb n="5" break="no"/>yani kumāruṁḍu kaṁnnama nāya 
<lb n="6" break="no"/>nigāru śrīviṣṇuprītigānurṁ 
<lb n="7"/>tama tallitaṁḍrikiṁnnitama Aṁnna 
<lb n="8"/>pedaAṁmnanāyaniṁ gāriki 
<lb n="9"/>puṁṇyaṁgā naḍabāvi travi 
<lb n="10" break="no"/>ṁcci rākaṭṭu kaṭṭiṁcci saupā 
<lb n="11" break="no"/>nālu gaṭṭiṁcci dharmma prati 
<lb n="12" break="no"/>ṣṭhasēsenu [<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>] maṁgaḷamahā śrī śrī śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> 
</p>

